{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n772\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 567 + 63 + 2 = 632\u2081\u2080\n\n858\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 648 + 45 + 8 = 701\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n632 \u00d7 701 = 632 \u00d7 (700 + 1) = 442,400 + 632 = 443,032\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n443032 \u00f7 9 = 49225 r 7\n49225 \u00f7 9 = 5469 r 4\n5469 \u00f7 9 = 607 r 6\n607 \u00f7 9 = 67 r 4\n67 \u00f7 9 = 7 r 4\n7 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 7\n\nReading from bottom to top: 744647\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n744647\u2089 = 7\u00d759049 + 4\u00d76561 + 4\u00d7729 + 6\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 7\u00d71\n= 413343 + 26244 + 2916 + 486 + 36 + 7\n= 443032\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n**744647**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 452}